{"tid":866824,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"呢隻保皇狗打手日日話反中,一到關鍵時候就收錢去大陸做野","createTime":"2018-10-18T07:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T04:17:00.000Z","uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac2442b971c8da87e632eb4c1d59430d010b867","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"雨革完<br />\n即刻去大陸做野<br />\n香港冇得做？<br />\n一做就四年<br />\n做完即刻來香港搞所謂抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/152944_e0186b7febae4fc2be72157d91c7ff78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F152944_e0186b7febae4fc2be72157d91c7ff78.png&h=4d8caefd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/152946_99f4a28b98e36d992b990ec18800c180.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F152946_99f4a28b98e36d992b990ec18800c180.png&h=b7511c7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"712bb7845681b37f5f4e0e364675f43a54d42d8b","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"仲要開分身又開錯ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n証明佢有分別去製造支持<br />\n同大陸一撚樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/153223_cc4983a8dac5831dfb1476f6aa000b30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F153223_cc4983a8dac5831dfb1476f6aa000b30.png&h=e46593b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83fa676589c0302293a5342fb10f4b1879de065b","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"自己去大陸做野就得天經地義<br />\n人地移民外國就失敗主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c268d087b6a74f04696e5b32ee3f7c2ea82331","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:37:52.000Z","msg":"自己去雨革完去大陸做野就理直氣壯<br />\n人地出post支持政黨就又五毛又打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一講唔掂就屈你冇出過街抗爭鍵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後吹自己出來貼貼紙<br />\n將其他人質疑當冇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c19954217fc208891863e5ca116b852535b307a","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"怎樣才能說服關愛座hunter<br />\n<br />\n1,<br />\n只要是關愛座hunter做 就必定正確<br />\n那怕他曾在雨革後關鍵時刻往中國工作四年，用淘寶，買中資<br />\n<br />\n2,<br />\n若然你現在移民 你便是散播失敗主義的五毛 (雨革後在中國工作四年的關愛座hunter不計算在內)<br />\n<br />\n3,<br />\n不論你提出什麼質疑，只要你沒有出來抗爭 你的質疑自動無效 <br />\n<br />\n4,<br />\n即使你曾經出來抗爭，他說你沒有 就是沒有 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5,<br />\n假若你支持關愛座hunter不喜歡的政黨<br />\n你便是打手五毛<br />\n即使他自己曾開分身而忘了轉帳號"},{"pid":"8dc1f9cca9f0ed3672c776ad160dc4a899ca545f","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfbc3941dd9ac0efc9c35b8900b0628f8d8c4d0","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79c91925897772204b209ef073f6bc54665fc81","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499385c26284f1939506ed445fc1f0efe0712b7f","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7872f195ae81426591df52774edff46027f97811","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關狗只係識不停推舊post<br />\n想洗走呢個post"},{"pid":"98ad4a0148066cbd2c5a22521115af240856952e","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"同一套道理<br />\n冇人入到來幫佢解釋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e4b9a341c71a013f289c7c8ef237a2c7ec5c4e","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對人不對事"},{"pid":"dbbcb8a7ee0d8256c55f8a3edc713e5a003be379","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又扮睇唔到了"},{"pid":"11a4295c197f3e9e9ee0376626896dcc6098b436","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"搵分身負評你就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c265f1db54bcc7e4bd436353c4540cc32bafd91","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又深潛"},{"pid":"42f32d7d5b6b1a54d6554cd975d52ee3b27a688e","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"笑死我<br />\n連回都唔敢回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd008d9f175de2662b498413c27dc45dcf5d7c0","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關狗呢"},{"pid":"7010753c3455eee0089a6698cb09700c007dcd18","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c91a79b7bc177083166db06983968ec90b520d","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"怎樣關愛座hunter才算賣港<br />\n<br />\n1,<br />\n只要是關愛座hunter做 就必定正確<br />\n那怕他曾在雨革後關鍵時刻往中國工作四年，用淘寶，買中資<br />\n<br />\n2,<br />\n若然你現在移民 你便是散播失敗主義的五毛 (雨革後在中國工作四年的關愛座hunter不計算在內)<br />\n<br />\n3,<br />\n不論你提出什麼質疑，只要你沒有出來抗爭 你的質疑自動無效 <br />\n<br />\n4,<br />\n即使你曾經出來抗爭，他說你沒有 就是沒有 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5,<br />\n假若你支持關愛座hunter不喜歡的政黨<br />\n你便是打手五毛<br />\n即使他自己曾開分身而忘了轉帳號<br />\n<br />\n6,<br />\n被別人質問為何雨革後一定要往大陸工作四年<br />\n不能回答時只能裝傻<br />\n不停推其他post<br />\n同時卻不停指責其他人是五毛<br />\n是轉移視線<br />\n卻不敢正面回答"},{"pid":"ddf6e30bc6cec7f22fbd07fe117a3398128a250a","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:43:07.000Z","msg":"只見負評<br />\n完全冇人可以幫佢解釋<br />\n佢自己都解釋唔到<br />\n睇來關狗都好識利用負評系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3729942a7fb842e3703c903e7c4aec26205baef","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303d08799a8287b6946029f916b5017d1b734e3f","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"搵個答都冇<br />\n你班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ce4b0fc5ad886a6911f371df2ba6a4be7d99d2","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1584ab45c47044771d4204f354ea5b711c154964","tid":866824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma